            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01Fp2HmjyWB3LMmPraGdd4J4\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Great question! After you launch your site, you'll get a live landing page that you can share with potential customers. You can share the link anywhere - social media, email campaigns, your podcast, etc. Plus, you'll be able to track visitor analytics, collect email signups, and make updates to your page anytime. The page is fully hosted and ready to go live immediately. Want to build it now and see what it looks like?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":4567,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":116,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
