            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 940,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_015QViPdZza5fYhASFWA3exQ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I don't have visibility into the specific UI layout of the Brand Personalization panel on your screen, but typically the logo upload option should be clearly labeled near the top of that panel. \\n\\nLook for something like:\\n- \\\"Logo\\\" section with an upload button\\n- \\\"Upload Logo\\\" or \\\"Add Logo\\\" \\n- An image upload area specifically for logos\\n\\nIf you're having trouble finding it, you can also just upload your logo in our chat here and I can make sure it gets included when we build your landing page. Would that be easier?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3069,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":119,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
