n. Defaults to 10.\"}},\"required\":[\"query_type\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"What is your business?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I have an idea for a business\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Basically, it will be for fitness\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I am a fitness trainer\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"I'm a trainer for men in their 50s, nobody caters to them\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your audience?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Men in their 50s\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"They've been told they're too old to get fit\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"Interesting, I need some more information! Can you tell me more about that?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Many of my clients have no experience with fitness, which is hard after a lifetime\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"That's awesome! And what about your solution?\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"My fitness program is specifically designed\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I can see you're starting to describe your solution! Can you tell me more about how your fitness program is specifically designed to help these men in their 50s? \\n\\nWhat makes your approach different from generic fitness programs, and how does it address their specific challenges (like being told they're too old, or ha