            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01E5Zm9nWgyiG6cugRSBZ6nP\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I understand you want to move quickly, but the core business idea is essential - I can't create effective marketing copy without knowing what your business actually does!\\n\\nLet me make this easier. Think about it this way:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need to understand your business idea to help you create a landing page. This is the foundation of everything.\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"I'm launching a meal prep service for busy parents that delivers pre-portioned ingredients with 15-minute recipe cards\\\",\\n    \\\"I run a consulting firm that helps SaaS companies reduce churn by implementing better onboarding flows\\\",\\n    \\\"I'm creating an online course teaching freelance designers how to raise their rates and attract premium clients\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What does your business do, and what makes it different from alternatives?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2568,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":197,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
