            "size": 2002,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01FmzETAd8ij6wfjEAE15qpJ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"helpMe\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"No problem! Let me help you break this down into clear pieces.\\\",\\n  \\\"template\\\": \\\"**Who are they?**\\\\n[Role/title] at [type of company/context] who [relevant situation or constraint]\\\\n\\\\n**What problems do they face?**\\\\n• [Specific frustration related to finding/booking guests]\\\\n• [Time or resource constraint]\\\\n• [Emotional impact - stress, anxiety, guilt, etc.]\\\\n\\\\n**What are they trying to achieve?**\\\\n• [Immediate goal - what they want their podcast to do]\\\\n• [Bigger aspiration - growth, authority, audience building]\\\\n\\\\n**Why don't current solutions work?** (optional)\\\\n[What they've tried and why it falls short]\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"**Who are they?** Podcast hosts at indie shows (5K-50K downloads/month) who produce weekly or bi-weekly episodes without a full production team\\\\n\\\\n**What problems do they face?**\\\\n• Spend 3-5 hours per episode just researching and cold-emailing potential guests\\\\n• Feel like they're bothering people with outreach and face high rejection rates\\\\n• Stressed about maintaining consistent publishing schedule when guests fall through\\\\n\\\\n**What are they trying to achieve?**\\\\n• Book engaging, credible guests who bring fresh perspectives to their audience\\\\n• Grow their show into a recognized voice in their niche and attract sponsors\\\\n\\\\n**Why don't current solutions work?** Manual outreach is time-consuming and unreliable; existing booking platforms are either too expensive or filled with low-quality guests looking for any exposure.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3064,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":400,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
