          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1473,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01SMFdR8uppSfH7ZGcJBfodh\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate your interest, but I need your input to create a landing page that truly represents YOUR unique business idea. I can't do this part for you because:\\n\\n1. **This is your business** - only you know what makes it special\\n2. **Generic pages don't convert** - I need your specific angle to write compelling copy\\n3. **This is the foundation** - everything else builds on this\\n\\nLet me make this super easy. Just answer this one question:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"What business idea do you want to test? It doesn't have to be perfect - just tell me what you're thinking.\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"I want to sell organic dog treats made with locally-sourced ingredients for health-conscious pet owners\\\",\\n    \\\"A meal prep service for busy parents that delivers pre-portioned ingredients with 15-minute recipes\\\",\\n    \\\"Custom hand-painted sneakers for people who want unique, wearable art\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Give me 1-2 sentences about your business idea. What do you do, and what makes you different?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2578,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":257,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
