            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2205,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01WEcWcRkKkk1B5vAqVB7qJh\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"helpMe\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Great question! Let me help you break this down into pieces.\\\",\\n  \\\"template\\\": \\\"**Who are they?**\\\\nMy ideal customers are [role/title] at [type of company/context] who [key characteristic about their situation].\\\\n\\\\n**What problems do they face?**\\\\nThey struggle with [specific pain point 1] and [specific pain point 2]. This makes them feel [emotional impact].\\\\n\\\\n**What are they trying to achieve?**\\\\nThey want to [concrete goal 1] and [concrete goal 2] so they can [bigger outcome they care about].\\\\n\\\\n**Why don't current solutions work?**\\\\n[What they're doing now] takes too much [time/money/effort] or [what's missing from alternatives].\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"**Who are they?**\\\\nMy ideal customers are podcast hosts running shows with 1,000-50,000 downloads per episode who are doing everything themselves or with a small team.\\\\n\\\\n**What problems do they face?**\\\\nThey struggle with spending 5-10 hours per week researching potential guests, sending cold emails that get ignored, and dealing with guests who cancel last minute. This makes them feel like they're wasting time on admin work instead of creating great content.\\\\n\\\\n**What are they trying to achieve?**\\\\nThey want to consistently book high-quality guests who bring fresh perspectives and keep their release schedule on track so they can grow their audience and establish their show as a go-to resource in their niche.\\\\n\\\\n**Why don't current solutions work?**\\\\nManually searching LinkedIn and Twitter is time-consuming and hit-or-miss. Guest booking agencies are expensive ($2,000+/month) and only work for big shows. Facebook groups and guest databases are full of low-quality pitches from people who haven't even listened to the show.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3260,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":453,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
          },
